{
  "text": "This eliminates two parameters from the fit. In addition, by making r 2 \u00bc 1, we eliminate one more so that the fitting process requires estimating 2p -2 parameters. The parameterization that we propose is slightly different from that used by [CITATION_1] , who estimated r but normalized the estimated functions so that the maximum scale value was unity.",
